    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to the wonderful world of <strong>Let's Pet Pets™</strong>! </h2><br>This is a game where you pet pets to gain <strong>Pet Points</strong>. <strong>Pet Points</strong> can be used to purchase <strong>Helping Hands</strong>. <strong>Helping Hands</strong> will give you more <strong>Pet Points</strong> automatically every second (even while you are away). Each <strong>Helping Hand</strong> can be individually upgraded to give you even more <strong>Pet Points</strong>. You can also use <strong>Pet Points</strong> to purchase <strong>Items</strong>. <strong>Items</strong> are unlocked through reaching milestones and progressing through your <strong>Let's Pet Pets™</strong> journey. These <strong>Items</strong> have a multitude of effects. From increasing the efficiency of manual pet petting to increasing the duration of the <strong>Pet Time Bonus</strong>. The <strong>Pet Time Bonus</strong> is a window of time which will multiply your <strong>Pet Point</strong> production across all sources. This <strong>Pet Point</strong> production multiplier will remain active for the duration of the <strong>Pet Time Bonus</strong>. As you pet pets, upgrade <strong>Helping Hands</strong>, purchase <strong>Items</strong>, and play <strong>Let's Pet Pets™</strong> you will complete <strong>Quests</strong>. <strong>Quests</strong> will earn you <strong>Heart Points</strong>. <strong>Heart Points</strong> are a very valuable resource because they let you get new eggs from the <strong>Pet Shop</strong>. <strong>Eggs</strong> can hatch into a new pet or upgrade a pet you already have. These <strong>Eggs</strong> hold a variety of cute animals ranging from <strong>Anteaters</strong> to <strong>Zebras</strong>. Each pet has its own unlockable <strong>Items</strong>, <strong>Quests</strong>, and even its own <strong>Helping Hands</strong>. You continue to gain <strong>Pet Points</strong> from other pets you have bought even while you are petting a different pet. If you feel progress slowing down and need a boost, you can <strong>prestige</strong>. Activating <strong>prestige </strong>will reset all your <strong>Helping Hands</strong> and <strong>Items</strong>, but you will keep your <strong>Eggs</strong>, <strong>Pets</strong>, <strong>Quests</strong>, and <strong>Upgrades</strong>. As you can clearly see, petting pets is going to be quite the adventure.",
